{"tid":627370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經民聯反對撤MPF對沖方案","createTime":"2018-04-13T02:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T02:40:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f42328ec09f62bbfdfda5ee8ae691f0bb2986d03","tid":627370,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360320?_ga=2.68928401.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360320%3F_ga%3D2.68928401.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=kpoCXumN%2Bb2CpWJgotjqcACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1eeed765\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360320%3F_ga%3D2.68928401.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=01453cff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360320?_ga=2.68928401.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n經民聯反對撤MPF對沖方案<br />\n<br />\n2.4K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180413/large/18653244.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180413%2Flarge%2F18653244.jpg&h=66cb49fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經民聯主席盧偉國<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府早前提出取消強積金對沖初步構思，勞工界反應正面，但商界仍拒絕收貨。經民聯昨發聲明反擊，指與工商界及中小微企代表多次磋商後，認為新方案有違政府、勞、資三方共同承擔的原則，對中小微企的長遠財務構成沉重壓力，嚴重損害香港的營商環境，促請政府在廣泛諮詢後才作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指政府漠視工商界訴求<br />\n<br />\n取消對沖新方案將補貼僱主的金額由79億元加碼至172億元，補貼期由10年延長至12年。但經民聯不滿政府沒提供詳細數據解釋172億元如何推算，加上整個方案設計複雜，僱主和僱員都無法清楚是否可行。對於延長補貼期，經民聯認為，除了首三年遣散費及長服金補貼比例一半不變外，政府繼續維持每年遞減的做法，完全漠視工商界要求政府作出長遠應有承擔的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯主席盧偉國批評，政府沒有解決企業在12年補貼期後的財政負擔問題，擔心企業會提早解僱員工；而在新方案下，僱主每月要額外供款1%，但長服金和遣散費的領取金額上限和計算比例卻無改變，較上屆政府方案倒退，絕不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局發言人指，政府現正收集商界及勞工界等主要持份者的意見，強調有關初步構思仍未是政府的決定，待收集持份者的看法後，政府都會盡力改良方案，希望勞資雙方本着互諒互讓的精神，早日敲定方案。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧文烈"},{"pid":"98b49cd000d5d27a8b096f7c3cf9386732b9eef5","tid":627370,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/101318_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F101318_74692c120bb7a45498c6a496432247ee.gif&h=6ff7bf2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47a9997e7989fda86edb61678a5fafd6c3ba1528","tid":627370,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"呢個垃圾正苦, 識改<span style=\"color: red;\">企業利得稅成兩級制<br />\n全民就業, 失業率偏低, 係種種有利爭取勞工權益情況下</span><br />\n無趁機會同企業傾勞工條件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港發生乜野事<br />\n<br />\n大把稅收, 盈餘下, <br />\n只要撥多d 錢落去MPF 對沖果度, 好快就成事<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾預算案, 搵個無能兼無腦會計佬去做財爺起劏房波</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而MPF 對沖<br />\n全民退保, 醫保<br />\n勞工假, 銀行假問題<br />\n立法5天工作制<br />\n最高工時<br />\n</span><br />\n呢d 實事, 隨時仲簡單又唔去做, 推都唔撚識推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2蚊乘車, 以前殖民地推既話, 點會由正苦比架<br />\n一定由港督由商界(太古 怡和 etc ) 帶頭自己做, <br />\n國泰工會點解咁強大, 都係當年前港英正苦要太古放權<br />\n<br />\n理財新哲學：無條件減利得稅, 免差餉<br />\n<br />\n長遠措施無樣野做到<br />\n有心攪樓市<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">租金管制</span>好應該推動出黎傾下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門都立法規定<br />\n強制性假日返工要「三工」<br />\n<br />\n香港法例仍然係講緊最少要比員工放勞工假咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民就業<br />\n帶頭無條件減利得稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bf77aa00a9372f78e00693d457968f02c54217","tid":627370,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"經民聯反政府即係搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1347ac43f369e522c3001670e6b38d840b0dd1","tid":627370,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"習總&mdash;-&gt;支持&mdash;-&gt;林鄭<br />\n<br />\n林鄭&mdash;-&gt;推&mdash;-&gt;取消MPF對沖方案<br />\n<br />\n經民聯反對方案=反對林鄭=反對京城任命既官=反習總=反國家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罪當處死"},{"pid":"0ec17e3c095ce917b574fce7df1ab08c5ccfb251","tid":627370,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf1347ac43f369e522c3001670e6b38d840b0dd1","tid":627370,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"習總&mdash;-&gt;支持&mdash;-&gt;林鄭<br />\n<br />\n林鄭&mdash;-&gt;推&mdash;-&gt;取消MPF對沖方案<br />\n<br />\n經民聯反對方案=反對林鄭=反對京城任命既官=反習總=反國家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罪當處死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"其實d商家唔係驚蝕，係驚賺得唔夠盡啫<br />\n呢d利民措施應要強制立法"},{"pid":"097bb6461ac7434709d1e48a042b0fd55770acce","tid":627370,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h